1
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:41,010
[Adapted from the novel
Sweet Sixteen by Zi Yue]

2
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:44,280
[Sweet Sixteen]

3
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:47,340
[Episode 2]

4
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:55,100
Weiran,

5
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:57,460
this is Ya,

6
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:58,540
who I mentioned.

7
00:00:58,900 --> 00:00:59,460
Ya,

8
00:00:59,860 --> 00:01:01,740
this is Qu Weiran,

9
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:03,220
the amazing senior I told you about.

10
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,860
He is good at everything.

11
00:01:05,060 --> 00:01:05,820
Right?

12
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,100
Hello.

13
00:01:07,780 --> 00:01:08,460
Yawang.

14
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:09,260
[Qu Weiran, Haide Enterprises' CEO]

15
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:10,340
Nice to meet you.

16
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:17,900
I heard you got an offer.

17
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:22,540
That's all thanks to you.

18
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:27,340
I have a jersey signed by Iverson.

19
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:29,100
You must take it.

20
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:31,620
When have you ever been so generous?

21
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:33,700
There is something.

22
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:35,780
My girlfriend

23
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:36,700
will be coming

24
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:38,220
to Haide Enterprises
for an interview in a few days.

25
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:39,580
Well...

26
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:41,620
we're so close...

27
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:42,220
right?

28
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:44,020
Isn't this something
you could help with?

29
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,860
Your girlfriend is so blessed.

30
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:50,860
If I were her,

31
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:52,940
I'd never be able to let you go.

32
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:55,220
Here's a gift for you too.

33
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:56,300
Thank you.

34
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,860
Your bracelet is unique.

35
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:08,980
Yes.

36
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,380
Weiran,

37
00:02:13,220 --> 00:02:14,140
nice to meet you!

38
00:02:14,540 --> 00:02:15,860
Thank you for looking out for Xiaotian.

39
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,020
I have an interview soon,
so please excuse me.

40
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:19,780
Yes, she has an interview.

41
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:21,700
Remember to take everything.

42
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,260
Good luck!

43
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:29,420
Weiran,

44
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,220
can I ask you something?

45
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:36,020
After I'm gone,

46
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:37,940
please help me

47
00:02:37,940 --> 00:02:39,220
to look out for Ya.

48
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,580
After all, she's alone here

49
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:41,460
so I'm worried.

50
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:44,940
You haven't told her yet?

51
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:49,060
I haven't figured out how to.

52
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:50,340
It's difficult

53
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,060
to broach the subject.

54
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:54,620
Don't worry.

55
00:02:57,420 --> 00:02:58,020
Leave it to me.

56
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:01,900
Thank you!

57
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:02,860
Thank you.

58
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,060
Let's watch a match tonight.

59
00:03:15,780 --> 00:03:16,700
For what?

60
00:03:17,140 --> 00:03:18,700
To celebrate!

61
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:19,620
I've sent it to you.

62
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,820
Okay. Well...

63
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:23,580
I have to make a trip to school.

64
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:24,380
I'll meet you there.

65
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:29,620
Xia Mu!

66
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:31,980
Things will get better for us!

67
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,060
Be careful!

68
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:37,900
I'll be fine.

69
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,100
[Haide Human Resources]

70
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:54,100
Hello?

71
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,340
Hello, Miss Shu.

72
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:57,060
Congratulations
on passing today's interview.

73
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:58,780
Welcome to Haide.

74
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:01,020
Please report for work next week
with your physical examination report.

75
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,980
The results are out so soon?

76
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,780
You're Mr. Qu's friend.

77
00:04:04,780 --> 00:04:05,540
Of course.

78
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:07,820
Mr. Qu?

79
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:09,260
Qu Weiran?

80
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:09,940
Yes.

81
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:11,820
We look forward to seeing you soon.

82
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,060
Thank you.

83
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:17,580
Xia Mu, something has come up.

84
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:18,340
I'll see you later.

85
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:37,060
Xia Mu, something has come up.

86
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:37,900
I'll see you later.

87
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:42,820
Here, give him one!

88
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:46,140
Nice one!

89
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:46,660
Tang Xiaotian!

90
00:04:47,660 --> 00:04:48,180
Ya.

91
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:49,260
You... Why are you...

92
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:51,780
No... I...

93
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:52,780
What is it?

94
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,540
Don't you know what you've done?

95
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:56,300
What did I do?

96
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:58,260
Why did you arrange
for me to work at Haide?

97
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,740
Don't you want to work there too?

98
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,060
Yes, I do.

99
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,980
I aimed to earn my job with my skills,

100
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:04,740
not by your intervention.

101
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:06,140
There's nothing wrong with that!

102
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,620
A boyfriend is supposed to support you!

103
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:09,220
I'm being serious.

104
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:11,180
Do you know what I want?

105
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,580
Let's not talk here.

106
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,620
Let's go.

107
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:17,700
Wait for me!

108
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,500
Don't go!

109
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:19,500
She's angry!

110
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,180
Go after her!

111
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,300
I'll deal with you guys later!

112
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:22,620
Wait for me!

113
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,380
♪Want to be closer♪

114
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:40,270
♪But the distance between us♪

115
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:44,150
♪Keeps changing♪

116
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,740
♪As unclear as if
we were looking through mist♪

117
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:48,580
Don't be afraid.

118
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,020
I'm here

119
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,460
with you.

120
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,940
♪Why♪

121
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:56,950
♪Can't I forget?♪

122
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:00,550
♪The answer has always been you♪

123
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:05,470
♪The reason my heart beats♪

124
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:09,950
♪If being together♪

125
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:13,990
♪Is the final ending♪

126
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,820
What do you mean I'm always like this?

127
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:17,980
I'm doing this for you!

128
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:19,460
Why are you making decisions for me?

129
00:06:19,460 --> 00:06:20,500
Aren't you the one who wants

130
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,300
to get into Haide?

131
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,220
I do,

132
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,580
but why did you have to do this?

133
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:24,700
Did I ask you to pull strings for me?

134
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:25,900
Fine, let's drop Haide for a minute.

135
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:27,460
Why did you behave that way
at the court today?

136
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,180
Are your friends more important than me?

137
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:31,710
♪And write this story again♪

138
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:33,220
The match is over?

139
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:35,150
♪I don't believe in fate♪

140
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,260
[Xia Mu. One message unread]

141
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:39,100
♪If I can hug you again♪

142
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:40,780
We're not done here.

143
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:42,100
Listen, I...

144
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:42,620
Xia Mu!

145
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:46,420
♪Let all our partings♪

146
00:06:46,420 --> 00:06:48,550
♪Indifference and struggles♪

147
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:51,870
♪Return to when we met♪

148
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:55,910
♪As the crowd disappears♪

149
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,230
♪It's still you♪

150
00:06:58,740 --> 00:06:59,620
You're still up?

151
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:02,390
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

152
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:05,980
You didn't wait
at the entrance for me, right?

153
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:09,540
I'm sorry.

154
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:11,420
Something unexpected happened today

155
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:12,580
so I didn't read your message.

156
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:14,500
I won't do that ever again.

157
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,620
You won't be angry with me, right?

158
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:20,660
You're the best.

159
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,140
Please.

160
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:30,980
I've never been your brother.

161
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,980
What do you mean by that?

162
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:36,180
Even if you're angry,
how can you say that?

163
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:39,900
If you let Mom hear that,

164
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:40,700
you'll be doomed!

165
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:04,060
♪Where's
the physical examination report?♪

166
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:04,940
♪Physical examination report...♪

167
00:08:08,170 --> 00:08:09,830
[To Mr. Xia Mu]

168
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:26,480
[Termination of Adoption Procedure]

169
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:32,260
Xiaotian,

170
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:33,660
I found
your brother-in-law's sketchbook.

171
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:34,140
Okay!

172
00:08:42,580 --> 00:08:43,860
I'm not trying to peek into it.

173
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:46,220
I'm just helping you check your work.

174
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:17,100
Xia Mu, where are you?

175
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:20,220
I'm in Art Room 3.

176
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:20,940
Xia Mu!

177
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:24,060
Tell me.

178
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,620
Do you have feelings for someone?

179
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:30,940
What's that got to do with you?

180
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,100
What has it got to do with me?

181
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:33,900
Of course it does!

182
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:38,740
Look at this!

183
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:47,220
This is between me and her.

184
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,220
It has nothing to do with you.

185
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,780
You and her?

186
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:53,300
Does she know?

187
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:55,260
I'm warning you.

188
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:57,180
Remember who you are.

189
00:09:58,380 --> 00:09:59,860
She's your sister.

190
00:10:01,620 --> 00:10:02,380
Do you hear me?

191
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:28,660
♪SO RE MI♪

192
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:34,140
♪I can't help thinking♪

193
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:37,940
♪A happy or sad ending♪

194
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:42,740
♪Is up to us♪

195
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:46,940
♪Lovers are always forced to part♪

196
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:50,860
♪How dramatic♪

197
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:55,420
♪Doing my best to run to you♪

198
00:10:56,060 --> 00:11:01,100
♪And our happy ending♪

199
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:03,900
♪If I can meet you again♪

200
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:06,180
♪And write this story again♪

201
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:10,140
♪I don't believe in fate♪

202
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:13,540
♪If I can hug you again♪

203
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,300
♪I don't care♪

204
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:18,620
♪About the bitter past♪

205
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:21,380
♪Let all our partings♪

206
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:23,460
♪Indifference and struggles♪

207
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:26,740
♪Return to when we met♪

208
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:30,380
♪As the crowd disappears♪

209
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:32,140
♪It's still you♪

210
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:38,500
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

211
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:42,100
♪If we start again♪

212
00:11:42,100 --> 00:11:43,970
♪Can our ending be changed?♪
